{"name": "v2dl-lite", "metadata": {"name": "v2dl-lite", "version": "0.1.1", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["beautifulsoup4", "cloudscraper"], "summary": "Add your description here", "upload_time": 1732544358}, "documentation": ["# V2DL-Lite  \n[English](/README.en.md)\n\n\u8d85\u7d1a\u8f15\u91cf\u7248\u672c\u7684 [V2PH-Downloader](https://github.com/ZhenShuo2021/V2PH-Downloader)\n\n## Why V2DL-Lite?  \n\u7528\u700f\u89bd\u5668\u81ea\u52d5\u5316\u5de5\u5177\u722c\u87f2\u89ba\u5f97\u5fc3\u6709\u4e0d\u7518\uff0c\u65bc\u662f\u5beb\u4e86\u4e00\u500b lite \u7248\u672c\u3002\n\n\u6b64\u7248\u672c\u79fb\u9664\u80a5\u5927\u7684\u81ea\u52d5\u5316\u5de5\u5177\uff0c\u6c92\u6709\u9ebb\u7169\u7684\u5bc6\u78bc\u8a2d\u5b9a\uff0c\u6c92\u6709\u773c\u82b1\u64a9\u4e82\u7684\u81ea\u5b9a\u7fa9\u9078\u9805\uff0c\u53ea\u8981\u6e96\u5099\u597d cookie \u6a94\u6848\u5373\u53ef\u8f15\u9b06\u4e0b\u8f09\u3002\n\n## Usage\n\n```sh  \npip install v2dl-lite  \nv2dl-lite <url or urls.txt>  \n```  \n\n\u8d85\u65b9\u4fbf\uff01\n\n## Cookie \u767b\u5165  \nCookie \u767b\u5165\u662f\u5fc5\u8981\u7684\uff0c\u4f7f\u7528 [Cookie-Editor](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/cookie-editor/hlkenndednhfkekhgcdicdfddnkalmdm) \u4ee5 **Netscape** \u683c\u5f0f\u532f\u51fa\u4e26\u4e14\u5132\u5b58\u5728\u8a2d\u5b9a\u8cc7\u6599\u593e\u4e2d (\u9810\u8a2d\u5728 `~/.config/v2dl`)\u3002\u8173\u672c\u6703\u81ea\u52d5\u6383\u63cf\u6240\u6709\u5305\u542b  \"**cookie**\" \u7684 **txt** \u6a94\u6848\u3002\n\n## \u9078\u9805  \n- `-s`: \u8df3\u904e\u5df2\u7d93\u5b58\u5728\u7684\u6a94\u6848 \n- `-d`: \u8a2d\u5b9a\u4e0b\u8f09\u8cc7\u6599\u593e (default: `~/Downloads/v2dl`).  \n- `-c`: \u8a2d\u5b9a cookies \u8cc7\u6599\u593e (default: `~/.config/v2dl`).  \n- `-l`: \u8a2d\u5b9a\u8a9e\u8a00\uff0c\u7528\u65bc\u547d\u540d\u4e0b\u8f09\u8cc7\u6599\u593e (default: `zh-TW`).  \n- `-v`: \u986f\u793a\u5957\u4ef6\u7248\u672c  \n\n## Notes  \n- \u652f\u63f4\u591a cookies \u6a94\u6848  \n- \u7db2\u7ad9\u7684\u6a5f\u5668\u4eba\u6aa2\u67e5\u5f88\u56b4\u683c\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u6b64\u7248\u672c\u53ef\u80fd\u9700\u8981\u5f88\u983b\u7e41\u7684\u66f4\u65b0 cookies\n"], "modules": [{"name": "v2dl_lite.constant", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "v2dl_lite.constant.BASE_URL", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "v2dl_lite.constant.BASE_DIR", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "v2dl_lite.constant.SLEEP_TIME", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "v2dl_lite.constant.SPEED_LIMIT_KBPS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "v2dl_lite.constant.UA", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "v2dl_lite.constant.HEADERS", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "v2dl_lite.version", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "v2dl_lite.version.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "v2dl_lite._types", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "v2dl_lite._types.DownloadConfig", "bases": [], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "v2dl_lite._types.DownloadConfig.httpx_sess", "type": {"name": "AsyncClient", "xref": {"fqname": "httpx.AsyncClient", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "v2dl_lite._types.DownloadConfig.download_dir", "type": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "v2dl_lite._types.DownloadConfig.semaphore", "type": {"name": "Semaphore", "xref": {"fqname": "asyncio.Semaphore", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "v2dl_lite._types.DownloadConfig.speed_limit_kbps", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "v2dl_lite._types.DownloadConfig.start_idx", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions